HEADWORD: Puff-leg
<hw>Puff"-leg`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any one of numerous species of beautiful humming birds of the genus
<gen>Eriocnemis</gen> having large tufts of downy feathers on the
legs.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

